CSS Selectors 
Website: https://www.amazon.in/ 

Search 'Laptop' using CSS ID → #twotabsearchtextbox. 
driver.findElement(By.cssSelector("#twotabsearchtextbox")).sendKeys("Laptop");

Click search button using CSS Attribute → input[value='Go']. 
driver.findElement(By.cssSelector("[value='Go']")).click();

Select the first product using nth-child CSS selector.
